snippet.title: Tsukimi Planet - A Wish From A Yandere (ALL ENDINGS), Manly Let's Play
snippet.description:
Tsukimi Planet is a Visual Novel written by Charon of Yanderella fame. It follows a boy on his death bed who is visited by a stranger from the moon...

Video contains all three endings.
